    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of May 9 article on hockey announcer Mike Emrick, which referred incorrectly to his experience with ABC Sports, who used him for four regular-season games</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The TV Sports column yesterday, about the hockey announcer Mike Emrick, referred incorrectly to his experience this year with ABC Sports. While he has broadcast none of the network's National Hockey League playoff games, he was indeed employed for four regular-season games.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>The TV Sports column yesterday, about the hockey announcer Mike Emrick, referred incorrectly to his experience this year with ABC Sports. While he has broadcast none of the network's National Hockey League playoff games, he was indeed employed for four regular-season games.</p>
      </block>
